/1356233</a><br />\n<br />\n[代出] 丁權？唔係無得斷 係有得搞<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1353811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1353811</a><br />\n<br />\n[新聞刺針] 兩區議員事前已通知警方，並截圖證明警方指「已有足夠人手應付」。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356477</a><br />\n<br />\n【上熱門呀】元朗遊行詳細po，推正經po啦，咪再講好多垃圾po<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356135</a><br />\n<br />\n侵：China could stop them , if they wanted<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dozHuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dozHuS</a>"},{"pid":"a3beff21a471f520c116a1b3b349d19c7eb8e5a1","tid":1356660,"uid":199709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>上環Video 整合 (粗略) (keep updating) </strong> 元朗有夠多片 我就淨係推上環喇 <br />\n麻煩各位巴絲幫手backup <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1209367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1209367</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348465/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348465/page/1</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1350647/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1350647/page/1</a>  <br />\n(最新片段) 尋晚警犬無舉旗下連開四槍以上 <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/349470836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F349470836&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=63f21fbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/349470836</a> <br />\n721 上環發生了什麼事？ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=2bX6CKzg_5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D2%26v%3D2bX6CKzg_5w&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=2e21e3c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=2bX6CKzg_5w</a> <br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=e15108dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a> <br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=d47fe044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a> <br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=068fded5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a> <br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=4a11ec62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a> <br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=02a7daa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a> <br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=61bfd85e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a> <br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=21382dac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a> <br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=474bdeb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a> <br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=1eff0126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a> <br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=008236a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a> <br />\n  <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=da9cf08a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a> <br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=9a7325a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a> <br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=e4c6527f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a> <br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=700f0456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a> <br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=c167d0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a> <br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplePhotographers%2Fphotos%2Fa.1131233677080155%2F1131269430409913%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=a0428d26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a> <br />\n7.21民陣大遊行 | 警方平射角度開槍清場 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEsy4jTTOpYI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=55dddaba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a> <br />\n有記者直接被催淚彈打中（07.21）譴責警察暴力：記者被催淚彈打中，係直接打中！ <a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTeVHAuMLP4&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=a800cae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4</a> <br />\n有義士腳部中槍 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157863977222448%3Fs%3D1279554103%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=b991a74f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a> <br />\n【2225 上環】警方施放多枚催淚彈，其後多部警車在警察防線後方鳴笛 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2513792761974182&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=3718ec6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182</a> <br />\n7.21 催淚彈在人群中爆開 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=446725156177245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D446725156177245&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=eb0043a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=446725156177245</a> <br />\n7.21 無證速龍向記者舉槍 亮警棍威嚇 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=370689103642714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D370689103642714&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=0baff808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=370689103642714</a> <br />\n7.21 警察開槍射胡椒彈 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=320505138857250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D320505138857250&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=2afbfc97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=320505138857250</a> <br />\n警再放催淚彈Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/471254926754367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F471254926754367%2F&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=f137c721\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/471254926754367/</a> <br />\n7.21 警察現場發放多枚催淚彈 22:20 Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F450544468858025%2F&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=76fb5a81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/</a> <br />\n速龍小隊斥記者「係咪中立、係咪有立場」Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F631475204017598%2F&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=5bd5cd26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fa